  "description": "Inverted drama. Begins at high synchrony (drama=0.7) and the S-curve arc drives the field DOWNWARD — partials drift apart, the voice dissolves, breath overtakes tone. A 15-second deconstruction. The star singer losing their voice, one partial at a time. Heartbreaking when played slowly.",
